{"tid":505214,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗狗之外，有無遇過啲好有靈性既野？","createTime":"2017-12-21T01:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T05:17:01.000Z","uid":21548,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1ae2c40b108609793d10b67956bf79723cc4e0fe","tid":505214,"uid":21548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:14:37.000Z","msg":"有人說，狗很有靈性，因為當牠們知道自己時日無多，將要死去的時候，會離開牠們的主人，獨個兒走到些偏遠地方令主人找不到自己，慢慢等死。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;在我的意見𥚃&quot;，不只狗這種動物有靈性，有些死物也有。以我之前在萬寧領養的純種Mentholatum為例，它們的壽命比較短，以致我帶了它出街不過數天，它已經離開了我。沙發底、櫃底、褲袋、外套袋等...我尋遍了全屋都未能找到它的蹤影，相信它已經到了遍遠地方，獨自度過生命中最後的時光了。<br />\n<br />\n而我，失去了Mentholatum的日子也不好過。沒有它，我被冷漠的冰凍天氣像抽濕機般抽走我唇上的水份。你問我會否再養另一隻Mentholatum?我不知道。至少，現在未有打算。因為我不知道自己還能否承受它離開我的感覺。"},{"pid":"ea38d1b4c4e42876e2889dc9092b2c11beff49d8","tid":505214,"uid":31048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26275bee193681d1862c8975653f0085cf391ee","tid":505214,"uid":21548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:18:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早晨"},{"pid":"b7c6fb52a3484ea66b09ea1478cc9368821f4409","tid":505214,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:19:43.000Z","msg":"牛，真係識流眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e98ca0a74248b2fd7f852e9ddfd418e8f7b74e8","tid":505214,"uid":78295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:28:23.000Z","msg":"牛熊証 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8a4b783b5120f0eda4305edcbe145639bad0ce","tid":505214,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:30:43.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"fca701841b7de257ed89eaa9a0f5c5aa2f20b62d","tid":505214,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:34:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>牛熊証 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢比人殺我會流淚，好似自己比人殺一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d65d3bbaabb9b2bf1fbc779c3ffb7729aee396","tid":505214,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:35:44.000Z","msg":"老鼠,識認主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab11ec682b86463db774867683fc9fbe933ef584","tid":505214,"uid":21548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:41:54.000Z","msg":"其實我只係想講我買咗曼秀雷敦潤唇膏幾日就唔見咗，同擦膠一樣，永遠喺你用完之前就唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32aecf805836e6e1e46f20db0f4c55a2fb2713a1","tid":505214,"uid":45998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:49:08.000Z","msg":"IVE仔 <br />\n<br />\n朝朝早葵芳港鐵站出口... 88C小巴站一車車將IVE仔送入青衣，佢地都好有靈性<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：IVE仔 （已畢業）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b858dac705548c7fb245a4b896cb99ba70e4fd0","tid":505214,"uid":50642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:52:41.000Z","msg":"IT同事"},{"pid":"e885cc84961e6b0a661aaf5d410ab6f127ce3aa6","tid":505214,"uid":163341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"我分享下我老豆遇過靈性海龜。老豆以前出海捕魚既 佢話有時會捕到d海龜上黎  跟住我老豆試過向住隻龜大聲話劏左你黎食。之後隻龜流眼淚喊 最後當然放生咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab2b2712af68cf516332bfd137b3c94f187287e","tid":505214,"uid":51585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:17:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其